## `.gitignore` ​:codex-file-citation[codex-file-citation]{line_range_start=1 line_range_end=28 path=.gitignore git_url="https://github.com/Donkopakad/Microlivetradeworked1/blob/main/.gitignore#L1-L28"}​

```gitignore
# Zig build outputs
.zig-cache/*
zig-out/*
kernel.o
simd.o
massif.*

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Local environment files with secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Runtime trade/log outputs
trade_history.csv
*.log

# OS/editor files
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
